'''倫敦書展'''（{{lang-en|London Book Fair}}），是每年4月於[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]舉行的大型國際圖書[[版權|版權]]交易會。

== 特点 ==
其為期三日規模僅次於[[德國|德國]][[法蘭克福書展|法蘭克福書展]]，至今發展成為逾100個國家和逾1,500家參展商參與的活動。倫敦書展創辦於1971年，於1985年由勵德展覽公司承辦，多年來多數在[[伯爵宮展覽中心|伯爵宮展覽中心]]舉行，亦曾經在[[倫敦展覽中心|倫敦展覽中心]]舉行。2020年3月4日，本年度书展因[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]疫情而取消<ref>{{Cite news|title=London Book Fair cancelled over coronavirus fears|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-51735208|newspaper=BBC News|date=2020-03-04|accessdate=2020-07-13|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720144651/https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-51735208|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=London book fair cancelled over coronavirus fears, amid growing anger|url=http://www.theguardian.com/books/2020/mar/04/london-book-fair-cancelled-over-coronavirus-fears-amid-growing-anger|accessdate=2020-07-13|date=2020-03-04|work=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018012055/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2020/mar/04/london-book-fair-cancelled-over-coronavirus-fears-amid-growing-anger|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=London Book Fair Canceled Over Coronavirus Fears|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/04/books/london-book-fair-coronavirus.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2020-03-04|accessdate=2020-07-13|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Alexandra|last=Alter|archive-date=2020-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305015235/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/04/books/london-book-fair-coronavirus.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

